data.description: This charming Cape Cod-style home offers a wonderful blend of comfort, character, and potential. Its four bedrooms, bonus room with vaulted ceilings, enclosed entryway, small music room, and finished basement provide versatile spaces for a variety of activities and lifestyles. As you enter, you're greeted by an enclosed entryway that provides a convenient transition space and helps keep the elements at bay. The main floor boasts a spacious dining room adjacent to a small music room, creating a perfect setting for entertaining guests or pursuing musical hobbies. The bonus room with vaulted ceilings adds a touch of elegance and versatility, providing ample space for a home office, playroom, or additional living area. The main level also encompasses a comfortable living room, where you can relax and unwind after a long day. The home offers four well-appointed bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests. Two bedrooms are on the upper level, offering privacy and a peaceful retreat for restful nights. A half bathroom on the upper level serves the bedrooms, while a convenient full bath is located on the main floor, ensuring everyone's comfort and convenience. The home offers four well-appointed bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests. The bedrooms are located on the upper level, offering privacy and a peaceful retreat for restful nights. A full bathroom on the upper level serves the bedrooms, while a convenient half bath is located on the main floor, ensuring everyone's comfort and convenience. The basement is fully finished, offering additional living space that can be utilized for various purposes, such as a recreation room, media room, or home gym. With outside access, the basement provides entry and exit, making it convenient for outdoor activities and storage. An added advantage is the setup for a full bathroom in the basement, giving the new owners the opportunity to customize and finish it according to their preferences and needs.
